=================================================================================
solr-jetty-maven
=================================================================================

A Solr project that runs in a Jetty/Maven context.


=================================================================================
Introduction
=================================================================================

To start Solr, type: mvn jetty:run-exploded
To use Solr's administrative UI, go to: http://localhost:8983/solr/admin


=================================================================================
Contact
=================================================================================

This is a pretty straightforword use of Solr, but if you have questions about it
feel free to contact me, Kevin S. Clarke, at ksclarke@gmail.com
